summary: Adds two small gates to Falkreath.
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds Stockade Gates to Falkreath! I found it slightly bizarre that the village had walls and a contingent of Guards, but it was left completely open for Bandits to stroll in and attack the village, well no more!

The latest version fixes the Dawnguard requirement, so you no longer need ANY DLC! I've also added a couple of Torches to the outer gates, so it's easier to see at night!
author: Lord Daem
